=head1 DESCRIPTION

Defines settings for a source data provider for a data migration.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 CDCStartPosition => Str

The change data capture (CDC) start position for the source data
provider.


=head2 CDCStartTime => Str

The change data capture (CDC) start time for the source data provider.


=head2 CDCStopTime => Str

The change data capture (CDC) stop time for the source data provider.


=head2 SlotName => Str

The name of the replication slot on the source data provider. This
attribute is only valid for a PostgreSQL or Aurora PostgreSQL source.



